	<h2><TMPL_VAR NAME="PAGE_TITLE"> Tips</h2>
	<p><strong>Dun & Bradstreet Records contain an overview about a business or government agency.</strong></p>

	<p>&nbsp;</p>
        <p>Find a Dun & Bradstreet record using one or more of the following search techniques:</p>
        <p>&nbsp;</p>

	<ol id="font81">
		<li>Search by Business Name and State. If too many records are returned, try adding a City.<br /><br /></li>
		<li>Search using the Business Address, City, and State. This can reveal other companies connected to the business.<br /><br /></li>
		<li>Search by the Telephone Number.<br /><br /></li>
		<li>Search by DUNS Number.<br/><br/></li>
	  </ol>
	<p>&nbsp;</p>


